River North, Chicago

A Luxurious Way of Living

2-6 bedroom apartments and penthouses available in the most beautiful building, located in a popular area of the city.
Prices Start at $749,900

Only 20 Apartments Left!

Different kind of lifestyle

Welcome to Sabay Towers

The Sabay Towers is a new residential complex by Richardson Development located at 949 Farland Street, River North, one of the most sought after neighborhoods in Chicago.The two luxurious 28-story towers present uncompromising construction standards and sophisticated modern design, which provides the highest quality of living that feels like a 5-star hotel.

The buildings, that were successfully occupied this summer contain 160 apartments and 4 stunning penthouses with breathtaking views of the city. There are very few apartments left and it's your last chance to invest or live in one of the most desirable buildings in Chicago. Request Showing

Watch The Live 360 Tour

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XHOmBV4js_E
Quality Life for You and Your Family

Compound
Amenities

The luxurious residential apartment block is designed to suit a modern lifestyle, and provides a spacious complex environment with everything you need. Stunning lobby with modern elevators, featuring security cameras for maximum safety.

Brilliant architectural design with breathtaking views of the city. A large, gorgeous fitness facility, indoor and outdoor pools, private underground parking, and an impressive green park that stretches over an area of 200 square meters.

Join other discerning property owners and choose from a variety of luxury apartments and penthouses made to the highest standards of construction and design.

All apartments incorporate sun balconies with breathtaking views of the city. They have porcelain granite flooring, modern kitchens, central air conditioners, solar water systems, private storage units, and ample parking. To receive a full specifications of available apartments and floor plans contact us today to schedule an appointment and tour.

Request Showing
Quality Life for You and Your Family

Your Dream Home Awaits You

Living in the Best Neighborhood in the City

The Location

The apartments are strategically located in the center of River North neighborhood, which is accessible to all main roads as well as shopping, sport, and leisure centers. The complex is within walking distance of the best schools and kindergartens. Join a quality community and upgrade your life so you can enjoy a prestigious, unapologetic, comfortable lifestyle.

item.title: Benefits
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
what makes us different

The values we live by

Quick & Efficient

We offer full-service tailored solutions for your move, including packing, transportation, and storage. We handle moves of any size with care, locally or long-distance. Trust us for a professional and comprehensive experience.

Safe-driven

We ensure your belongings are transported safely and securely. Our experienced team provides top-quality moving services, handling your possessions with care from start to finish. We have the necessary resources to manage any move, delivering your items in pristine condition to your destination.

Value-first approach

Doha Quick Mover offers exceptional moving services with a dedicated team that ensures your belongings are safely transported to your new home. We provide affordable prices without compromising on quality. Choose us for a hassle-free moving experience.

collaboration

Moving? Don't panic! Our team will make your move smooth with customized plans. Doha Quick Mover collaborate with you at every step, from packing to transportation and even unpacking. Rest easy knowing that you're in good hands and your move will be a positive experience.

item.content:encoded:
Reliable and Efficient Moving Solutions for all your Shifting Needs.

Schedule a free consultation with our team and let's make your move happen!

contact us
Quick Service Request

Send Your Moving Request

About Company

Professional Mover and Shifter

Welcome to our Mover and Shifting company based in Doha, Qatar. We are a team of professionals dedicated to providing top-quality moving and shifting services to our clients. With years of experience, we understand that moving can be stressful, but our goal is to make it as seamless as possible for you. Our team is highly skilled in handling everything from residential to commercial moves, locally or internationally. We are committed to being responsive and efficient, ensuring that your move is completed with the utmost care and professionalism. Our services include packing and unpacking, loading and unloading, and transportation of your belongings. We pride ourselves on our commitment to our clients and their satisfaction, which is why we go to great lengths to provide excellent customer service. Contact us today to discuss your moving and shifting needs and let us assist you with a stress-free move.

  • Certified Company
READ MORE

9+

Years In Business

1k+

Happy Clients

980

Projects Completed

36

Trained Staff

Our Services

We Provide Superior Moving Services

Home Sifting

Moving to a new home can be exciting, but it can also be an overwhelming task. Let our expert team handle your home shifting needs with ease and efficiency.

  • Read More
Office Relocation

Trust us to handle your office relocation with utmost professionalism and efficiency. we are equipped to ensure a seamless transition of your office to its new location.

  • Read More
Personal Packing

Our team of professionals offers guidance and assistance to ensure that your items are packed and transported safely and efficiently.

  • Read More
Additional Services

We Also Offer

We offer more than just loading and unloading trucks. Our packing, storage, and cleaning services make your move stress-free. We pack and handle fragile items, electronics, and large furniture with ease. Our secure storage facilities provide extra space while our cleaning services take care of the mess at your old place. Contact us for more information.

  • Furniture Installment
  • Cleaning Service
  • Interior Management
  • Storage Facility
  • Boxing and Unboxing items.
Know More
Why Choose Us

Six Reasons For People Choosing Us

Quality Service

Service that exceeds our customers' expectations.

Accredited

We have experience, expertise, and a commitment to excellence.

Trained Workers

Trained workers who specialize in packing and handling techniques.

Time Availability

We offers flexible scheduling options for our clients.

Quick Response

We're always here to help and support, when you need us.

Complete Security

We ensures complete security of your belongings.

We Are Business Who Cares, And it Shows

5 STARS REVIEWS AND CLIMBING

Rate Us on Google

Always appreciate your review.

People Say The Nicest Things

We are always happy to see what our clients are saying about us.

They provided exceptional service from start to finish. Their team was friendly, efficient, and took great care in handling all of my belongings. I highly recommend them for anyone in need of reliable and stress-free moving services.

Lorry Melon

Thank God I found them on time. Thanks to the Homestead community to help him go.

Steve Smith

Elora

One of the best movers in town. I loved their demeanor and how they treat people in general.

Amazing service and even more impressive behaviour. I liked their management system.

krista

Don't Know What To Start With?

Get A Solutions For All Moving Services

Offices

Head Office

We can handle any type of move, including long-distance. Contact us for a quote to make your move seamless and efficient.

Doha, Qatar

Phone: +974 3396 3144

Email: hossainshahrier.sh@gmail.com

Free Consultation

Get A Free Quote

item.content:encoded:
About Company

Professional and Expert Mover and Shifter

At Doha Quick Movers, we understand that moving can be a daunting and stressful experience. That's why we're dedicated to providing our customers with a smooth, seamless, and stress-free relocation process. From packing and loading to unpacking and arranging your furniture, we handle every aspect of your move with expertise and care.

Our Commitment to Quality

We are committed to providing our customers with the highest quality of service. Our team is experienced, trained, and dedicated to ensuring your satisfaction. We use high-quality materials and equipment to protect your belongings, and we maintain a fleet of well-maintained vehicles to ensure safe and efficient transportation.

Need help? Contact us

Phone: +974 3396 3144

Our History

Superior Moving Services

2014 - 2023

Our Most Efficient Year

Over the years, we have developed a deep understanding of the unique challenges and requirements of moving in Doha. We are well-versed in the local regulations, customs, and traffic patterns, and we have a network of trusted partners to provide additional services such as cleaning and handyman work.

Why Choose Us

Reason For Choosing Us

Accredited Company

We have experience, expertise, and a commitment to excellence.

Know More
Complete Security

We ensures complete security of your belongings.

Know MOre
Quality Service

We have experience, expertise, and a commitment to excellence.

Know MOre

Effortlessly Relocate to Your New Home with Doha Quick Moving Service

Home Shifting

Doha Quick moving, simplifies the daunting task of home shifting. Our experienced movers handle all types of household items with care, using high-quality packing materials to protect your belongings during transit. We offer end-to-end solutions for loading, unloading, disassembling and reassembling furniture, and unpacking. Trust us to make your home shifting process seamless and stress-free.

Scheduling An Appointment

Improve your efficiency by choosing us.

item.title: Packings
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
We'll help you pack efficiently, for a efficient move.

Our Doha quick mover company specializes in efficient and reliable packing solutions, we ensure your belongings are properly secured and packed to withstand long distance travel while preserving their quality and condition.

Checklist

We sort through your belongings and decide what needs to be packed. Ensure all items are properly packed and labeled with the room they belong to.

Decluttering

We simplifies the moving process with professional packing and decluttering services. Experts help customers sort and organize their belongings.

Furniture Packing

Our furniture packing service ensures that your valued furnitures are well-protected during transportation. Our team will carefully wrap, box, and secure your furniture to ensure a safe and secure move.

Supplies Packing

We provide reliable and efficient packing services for all your needs. We handle fragile glassware and bulky furniture with expertise, using top-quality materials to protect your items for the journey ahead.

what makes us different

The values we live by

Quick & Efficient

We offer full-service tailored solutions for your move, including packing, transportation, and storage. We handle moves of any size with care, locally or long-distance. Trust us for a professional and comprehensive experience.

Safe-driven

We ensure your belongings are transported safely and securely. Our experienced team provides top-quality moving services, handling your possessions with care from start to finish. We have the necessary resources to manage any move, delivering your items in pristine condition to your destination.

Value-first approach

Doha Quick Mover offers exceptional moving services with a dedicated team that ensures your belongings are safely transported to your new home. We provide affordable prices without compromising on quality. Choose us for a hassle-free moving experience.

collaboration

Moving? Don't panic! Our team will make your move smooth with customized plans. Doha Quick Mover collaborate with you at every step, from packing to transportation and even unpacking. Rest easy knowing that you're in good hands and your move will be a positive experience.

item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:

Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)

...or something like this:

The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.

As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Privacy Policy
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Who we are

Suggested text: Our website address is: http://localhost/wordpress.

Comments

Suggested text: When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor’s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.

An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.

Media

Suggested text: If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.

Cookies

Suggested text: If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.

If you visit our login page, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.

When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select "Remember Me", your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.

If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.

Embedded content from other websites

Suggested text: Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.

These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.

Who we share your data with

Suggested text: If you request a password reset, your IP address will be included in the reset email.

How long we retain your data

Suggested text: If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.

For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.

What rights you have over your data

Suggested text: If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.

Where your data is sent

Suggested text: Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.

item.title: Refund and Returns Policy
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
This is a sample page.

Overview

Our refund and returns policy lasts 30 days. If 30 days have passed since your purchase, we cant offer you a full refund or exchange.

To be eligible for a return, your item must be unused and in the same condition that you received it. It must also be in the original packaging.

Several types of goods are exempt from being returned. Perishable goods such as food, flowers, newspapers or magazines cannot be returned. We also do not accept products that are intimate or sanitary goods, hazardous materials, or flammable liquids or gases.

Additional non-returnable items:

  • Gift cards
  • Downloadable software products
  • Some health and personal care items

To complete your return, we require a receipt or proof of purchase.

Please do not send your purchase back to the manufacturer.

There are certain situations where only partial refunds are granted:

  • Book with obvious signs of use
  • CD, DVD, VHS tape, software, video game, cassette tape, or vinyl record that has been opened.
  • Any item not in its original condition, is damaged or missing parts for reasons not due to our error.
  • Any item that is returned more than 30 days after delivery

Refunds

Once your return is received and inspected, we will send you an email to notify you that we have received your returned item. We will also notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund.

If you are approved, then your refund will be processed, and a credit will automatically be applied to your credit card or original method of payment, within a certain amount of days.

Late or missing refunds

If you havent received a refund yet, first check your bank account again.

Then contact your credit card company, it may take some time before your refund is officially posted.

Next contact your bank. There is often some processing time before a refund is posted.

If youve done all of this and you still have not received your refund yet, please contact us at {email address}.

Sale items

Only regular priced items may be refunded. Sale items cannot be refunded.

Exchanges

We only replace items if they are defective or damaged. If you need to exchange it for the same item, send us an email at {email address} and send your item to: {physical address}.

Gifts

If the item was marked as a gift when purchased and shipped directly to you, youll receive a gift credit for the value of your return. Once the returned item is received, a gift certificate will be mailed to you.

If the item wasnt marked as a gift when purchased, or the gift giver had the order shipped to themselves to give to you later, we will send a refund to the gift giver and they will find out about your return.

Shipping returns

To return your product, you should mail your product to: {physical address}.

You will be responsible for paying for your own shipping costs for returning your item. Shipping costs are non-refundable. If you receive a refund, the cost of return shipping will be deducted from your refund.

Depending on where you live, the time it may take for your exchanged product to reach you may vary.

If you are returning more expensive items, you may consider using a trackable shipping service or purchasing shipping insurance. We dont guarantee that we will receive your returned item.

Need help?

Contact us at {email} for questions related to refunds and returns.

our services

Custom Moving Solutions

Home Shifting

We offer reliable and efficient home shifting services. Our experienced professionals carefully pack and load your belongings and have a fleet of well-maintained moving trucks. We will unload, unpack, and place your items in the rooms you desire at your new home. Learn More

Office Moving

We offer office relocation services with planning, packing, disassembly and reassembly of furniture and equipment, loading and transportation, and post-move cleanup. We manage every aspect of your office relocation to minimize disruptions and ensure a smooth transition to your new location. Learn More

Custom Packing

We offer professional packing with high-quality materials for secure transit. Custom options are available for fragile and valuable items. Our experienced movers load and unload carefully for a smooth and hassle-free move. Choose our Packing Service for worry-free moving. Learn More
